			<div id="post-38" class="post-38 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized">
			<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="index.html?p=38" title="Permalink to Rental registry proposed in Springfield, Vermont" rel="bookmark">Rental registry proposed in Springfield, Vermont</a></h2>

			<div class="entry-meta">
				<p class="slug">Posted April 2, 2013 <!--by admin--></p>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

				<div class="entry-content">
				<p><a href="http://www.vhfa.org/about/news/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Springfield.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-9070" style="border: 0pt none; float: right; padding-left: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px;" title="Springfield" src="http://www.vhfa.org/about/news/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Springfield.jpg" alt="" width="354" height="215" /></a>A new registry listing all Springfield apartment buildings was proposed Monday night, according to the March 26, 2013 Barre Montpelier Time Argus.  </p>
<p>One of the driving factors behind the registry is fire safety.   The article describes the challenges that face fire fighters who arrive at a building and do not know how many households might be inside. </p>
<p>Read more on the <a href="http://www.vtaffordablehousing.org/news/2013/03/rental-registry-ordinance-proposed-in-springfield/">Vermont Affordable Housing Coalition&#8217;s web site</a>.</p>
							</div><!-- .entry-content -->
	
			<div class="entry-utility">
									<p class="postFooter"><span class="cat-links">
						Posted in <a href="index.html?cat=1" rel="category">Uncategorized</a>					</span>
					<!--<span class="meta-sep">|</span>-->
												<!--<span class="comments-link"><a href="http://www.rentalcodes.org/news/?p=38#respond" title="Comment on Rental registry proposed in Springfield, Vermont">Leave a comment</a></span>-->
