			<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="index.html?p=22" title="Permalink to Comments on proposed VT fire and building safety codes due Oct. 1" rel="bookmark">Comments on proposed VT fire and building safety codes due Oct. 1</a></h2>

			<div class="entry-meta">
				<p class="slug">Posted September 12, 2012 <!--by admin--></p>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

				<div class="entry-content">
				<p><a href="http://www.vhfa.org/about/news/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Blog_Background.jpg"><img class="alignnone  wp-image-7243" style="padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 10px; float: right; border: 0pt;" title="fire_code" src="http://www.vhfa.org/about/news/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Blog_Background.jpg" alt="" width="347" height="232" /></a>Vermont&#8217;s Division of Fire Safety has issued the proposed<a href="http://firesafety.vermont.gov/sites/firesafety/files/pdf/Code%20Info%20Sheets/2012_firecode.pdf"> 2012 Vermont Fire and Building Safety Code</a>.</p>
